{"word":"Pharez","slug":"pharez","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Pharez</b> <a href=\"#/H6557\">H6557</a> <br/> Called also Perez and Phares.<br/> A twin son of Judah by Tamar<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=38&verse=29'>Gen 38:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=2&verse=4'>1Ch 2:4</a><br/> Children of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=46&verse=12'>Gen 46:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=26&verse=21'>Num 26:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=2&verse=5'>1Ch 2:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=9&verse=4'>1Ch 9:4</a><br/> Children of, return from the captivity<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=11&verse=4'>Neh 11:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=11&verse=6'>Neh 11:6</a><br/> In the lineage of Jesus<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=1&verse=3'>Mat 1:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=3&verse=33'>Luk 3:33</a>"}]}